<h1 class="sm:text-3xl text-2xl font-medium title-font mb-4 text-gray-900">Contact</h1>
<section class="text-gray-600 body-font">
  <div class="container mx-auto flex px-5 py-12 md:flex-row flex-col items-center">
    <div class="lg:max-w-lg lg:w-full md:w-1/2 w-5/6 mb-10 md:mb-0">
      <%= image_tag "chillfiltr_hemp_parchment.png", class:"object-cover object-center rounded"  %>
    </div>
    <div class="lg:flex-grow md:w-1/2 lg:pl-24 md:pl-16 flex flex-col md:items-start md:text-left items-center text-center">
      <h1 class="title-font sm:text-4xl text-3xl mb-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Editor-in-chief
        <br class="hidden lg:inline-block">Krister Axel
      </h1>
      <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">CHILLFILTR® was built for one simple reason: to bring a spotlight to independent artists from around the world. With careful curation for CHILLFILTR® Radio & daily coverage of our favorite releases we strive to bring the best new art to a worldwide audience—by leveraging best-in-class technology to create a seamless and immersive web experience.</p>
	  <p>Hire me for your next <%= link_to "Webflow migration", pages_webflow_migration_path, class: "hover:text-white bg-teal-300" %>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="text-gray-600 body-font">
  <div class="container mx-auto flex px-5 py-24 md:flex-row flex-col items-center">
    <div class="lg:max-w-lg lg:w-full md:w-1/2 w-5/6 mb-10 md:mb-0">
      <%= image_tag "chillfiltr-ai.png", class:"object-cover object-center rounded"  %>
    </div>
    <div class="lg:flex-grow md:w-1/2 lg:pl-24 md:pl-16 flex flex-col md:items-start md:text-left items-center text-center">
      <h1 class="title-font sm:text-4xl text-3xl mb-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Submissions
      </h1>
      <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">You may use <%= link_to("this form", pages_submit_path, :class => "hover:text-white bg-teal-300") %> to submit music. Music that we like will be added to our radio channel and possibly broadcast on <a href="https://kskq.org" target="_blank" class="hover:text-white bg-teal-300">KSKQ</a>.</p>
	  <p>Pricing: <%= link_to "$2 per file", pages_submit_path, :class => "hover:text-white bg-teal-300" %>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

